{
 "name": "RPlog_SW1_Log_2000-06-15-1",
 "title": "Bazil Returns to the Deliverance",
 "summary": "Cleared of the trumped-up charge that he plotted to murder a captured Moff, Bazil McKenzie returns to the NRSC Deliverance in civilian clothes and reunites with old shipmates on the Ship Services deck. He trades barbed banter with the Quarren technician Kelvis Aquatica and meets the green Ghost Squadron trainee Vek Eldar, who is starstruck to learn he is shaking the hand of the famous former Ghost 5 pilot. The pilot Kierv -- of Draco Squadron -- joins them, and the group debates the looming Death Star threat, why the Empire wasted Gastus instead of striking Coruscant, and Emperor Valak's motives. Bazil, hiding his true Intelligence role, downplays his Coruscant contacts and resolves to win back his old executive officer slot, then heads off to crash in the guest quarters after asking the others where to find Colonel Altair Quila.",
